OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,FHammersmith Bridge could remain
OL,8,Fpermanently closed to cars after a
OL,9,Freport concluded repairs were not
OL,10,Ffinancially viable.
OL,12,FHammersmith & Fulham Council said a
OL,13,Ffull restoration would cost #300
OL,14,Fmillion and would effectively involve
OL,15,Fbuilding a new bridge.
OL,17,FThe crossing closed in 2019 after
OL,18,Fcracks were found in its cast-iron
OL,19,Fstructures, and the council has since
OL,20,Fspent #54 million so that it could be
OL,21,Fused by pedestrians and cyclists.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
