OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1783521452
OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,FThe council's full report said there
OL,8,Fwas "no financial option available"
OL,9,Fthat would allow for its full
OL,10,Frestoration.
OL,12,FUnder a settlement agreed by the
OL,13,Fprevious government, Hammersmith &
OL,14,FFulham Council would pay a third of
OL,15,Fthe total cost, with Transport for
OL,16,FLondon and the Department for
OL,17,FTransport covering the remaining two-
OL,18,Fthirds.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
