OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,F"The council's position, in line with
OL,8,Fthis one-third principle, is that it
OL,9,Fis still owed money by TfL, primarily,
OL,10,Fand the DfT towards the #54 million
OL,11,Fthat has been spent on the restoration
OL,12,Fproject," the report said.
OL,14,FLocal Labour MP Fleur Anderson said
OL,15,Fshe was "deeply disappointed", adding:
OL,16,F"I have fought hard for the reopening
OL,17,Fand will carry on.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@IO]wD@IOUwD@]O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
