CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1783521452
OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,F"Hammersmith & Fulham Council has
OL,8,Falready invested #54 million in
OL,9,Frepairs to ensure the safety of the
OL,10,Fbridge, and it is unreasonable to
OL,11,Fexpect them to bear additional
OL,12,Ffinancial burdens.
OL,14,F"I will continue to advocate for the
OL,15,Fcomplete restoration of Hammersmith
OL,16,FBridge."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@HO]
