OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Transport for
OL,8,FLondon said: "The London Borough of
OL,9,FHammersmith & Fulham owns and is the
OL,10,Fhighway authority for Hammersmith
OL,11,FBridge.
OL,13,F"We continue to work with the borough,
OL,14,Fthe Department for Transport and
OL,15,Fothers to agree the right solution, as
OL,16,Fwell as how any future works to the
OL,17,Fbridge might be funded."
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
