CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1783521452
OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,8,FTransport added: "We have provided #17
OL,9,Fmillion to keep the bridge open for
OL,10,Fwalking and cycling, and will continue
OL,11,Fto work closely with the council and
OL,12,FTransport for London as we consider
OL,13,Ffuture funding through our new
OL,14,FStructures Fund."
OL,16,FThe Structures Fund is a government
OL,17,Fscheme to help repair or replace major
OL,18,Flocal highway structures in England,
OL,19,Fincluding bridges, flyovers, tunnels
OL,20,Fand collapsed roads.
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@QO]
