OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1783521452
OL,3,CHammersmith Bridge may never reopen to
OL,4,Ccars because of lack of money for
OL,5,Crepairs
OL,7,FHowever, the deadline for projects to
OL,8,Fbe completed is 31 March 2030, which
OL,9,Frules out a full restoration.
OL,11,FInstead, the council has been advised
OL,12,Fby the Department for Transport to
OL,13,Fsubmit a bid for phased repairs. This
OL,14,Fwould keep the bridge open for
OL,15,Fpedestrians, cyclists and river
OL,16,Ftraffic.
